Amarillo has since been charged with two counts of first-degree murder and criminal possession of a weapon.

Law enforcement sources told the Post that Amarillo confessed to killing the two women who he said were 'doing voodoo on him'.

Investigators recovered a bloody hammer on the scene which they believe Amarillo used to bash in the heads of the two women.

